name: Sphere of Mirrors - 3D Digital Print
description:
This is the first 3D Digital Print that Z23 Studios has offered. This print titled "Sphere of Mirrors" is 12 x 18 inches printed on Single Matboard.

The print will be printed and/or framed (if you have purchased the framed option) and shipped out the following week.

name: Z23 Studios - Stickers
description:
Z23 Studios - Sticker: is part of the first campaign that Z23 Studios has offered, "The Gas Card Giveaway". Purchase one of these stickers for $2.00 to qualify for the contest.
Just display the sticker on your vehicle or in the back window of a vehicle. Then, follow us on Twitter: @Z23Studios. Remember this will happen the 23rd of the month ONLY. We will announce our location for that day via Twitter the 22nd before the giveaway. The twitter post will happen between 12 noon - 3pm.

The Giveaway will Start July 23, 2012 till November 23, 2012. The prize for those displaying the Z23 Studios Sticker is a $25.00 gas card. A minimum of 1 and a maximum of 5 prizes will be given on that day. Only 1 prize per winner. Prizes are based on a first come first serve basis. As an added perk, All people that purchase a sticker from the Z23 Studios Store will be automatically entered to win a $100.00 gas card. Drawing will occur on the 23rd of December. A little something for the holidays. Good Luck & I hope you win!!
